Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.70,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}自己能做到什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:38.48,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}有出乎意料的变故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:43.60,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一定能够越过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.73,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}power of dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:48.97,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一切从0开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:54.45,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}闪耀着飞向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:56.25,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}light blue wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:59.42,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}下定决心展翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:05.83,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}用最美的笑容  出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:10.91,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}现在向未知的世界起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:17.23,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}未来的选择  做决定的是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.63,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}去追逐梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.19,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}也会有想哭的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:26.84,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}那是最重要的愿望  不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:31.71,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一定能和明天的你再次相见
